-- Rio CEO says BHP bid undervalues Rio
-- 
-- Mon Nov 26, 2007 1:52am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/26/us-riotinto-bhpbilliton-ceo-idUSSYU00356020071126

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - Rio Tinto Ltd/Plc ( RIO.AX )( RIO.L ) Chief Executive Tom Albanese said on Monday that a $120 billion takeover bid by rival BHP Billiton Ltd ( BHP.AX ) fundamentally undervalues Rio. 

 Albanese also told an investor briefing that Rio was well placed to deliver value as a stand-alone firm. (Reporting by  James Regan )